# Gothic Lock Breaker — src hard invariants

Architecture, commands, and boundaries: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md).

## Bootstrap and performance

- Defer analytics: `src/analytics/posthog-init.js` + dynamic `import("./analytics/index.js")` after first render
- Lazy-load `onboarding.js` on cold landing only; use `onboarding-stub.js` for returning/hash users
- English locale is bundled in `i18n.js`; other locales fetch `locales/*.json`

## View and i18n

- View layer (`view.js` barrel + `view/*.js`): render only; handlers via arguments; **no module imports `store.js`** (now `core/store.js`)
- Tier C keys: all four locale files; respect `FROZEN_KEYS` in `i18n.js`
- Use `t()` / `tCount()`; never hardcode copy in the view layer for localized surfaces

## Analytics and assets

- Events through `src/analytics/`; transport only in `transport.js`
- Mobile-first; walkthrough grids use `minmax(0, 1fr)` — tests guard horizontal scroll
- Static assets via `public/` symlinks; do not reintroduce `vite-plugin-static-copy`
- Self-hosted Cinzel in `assets/fonts/`; no Google Fonts CDN
